high_descs: Turn around, enter into the room, find the diningtable and stand on its left side.
Pick up the bread from the table.
Turn backwards and locate the microwave.
Open it, put the loaf of bread in it, close it and take it out after some time.
Turn around and stand facing the fridge.
Place the loaf of bread into the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Find and heat the bread and place it in the fridge.

high_descs: Go to the diningtable on the left side. Stand in front of the diningtable.
Open the microwave door. Place the bread on the left side.  Close the door. Turn on the microwave for three seconds. Open the door. Take out the bread. Close the door.
Open the fridge door. Place the bread on the third level. Close the door.
anns.task_desc: Find a loaf of bread, heat it in a microwave and place it inside a fridge.
